items.name: Ashley Resch
items.description:
Ashley Resch is a Canadian model and social media celebrity.

This TI has been updated! Please check the "About this version" section for more info about training.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Do you have a specific idea for a TI in mind? Visit my website and let me know.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of beautiful (ashresch-125:0.99), a woman with beautiful blonde hair, hair upsweep updo, as a movie star in a (movie premiere), premiere gala, (near a movie theatre), natural skin texture, (sexy tight {red|yellow|blue|green|black|turquoise} strapless dress), 24mm, 4k textures, soft cinematic light, adobe lightroom, photolab, hdr, intricate, elegant, highly detailed, sharp focus, ((((cinematic look)))), soothing tones, insane details, intricate details, hyperdetailed, low contrast, soft cinematic light, exposure blend, hdr, faded, (paparazzi in background), (painted lips:1.1), ((looking at viewer:1.1))"

items.name: 学校 School Building Scenery LoRA
items.description:
日本の小中高の校舎っぽい風景を再現するLoRAです

LoRA reproduces a scene that looks like a Japanese elementary, junior high, and high school building.

　　

既存のモデルも学校の教室を描いたり出来るのですが、もっと日本の学校の風景をイラストにしたいと思ったのでこのLoRAを作りました

I wanted to illustrate more of a Japanese school scene, so I created this LoRA.

　

Example prompt:

教室(classroom)：

kyoushitsu, classroom, indoors, school chair, school desk, chalkboard, window, ceiling light, curtains, tree

(アイテムを並べることで教室っぽくなります。省くことで不要なアイテムを描かない事も可能…かもしれません）

　

廊下(hallway)：

rouka, scenery, hallway, window, indoors, door, building, school, sunlight

（building→別の校舎、他にもtreeで校内の樹木とか見えるとリアルっぽくみえます。必須ではないのでトリガー以外はお好みで加減してください。学習の影響で勝手に描く可能性もあります）

　

階段(stairs)：

kaidan, stairs, scenery, indoors, sunlight, window

（Weight上げないと木造校舎の階段になったりします。←それはそれで魔法学校みたいで良いのですが）

（あまり日本の校舎では見ないレイアウト配置だったり、構造的に変な階段がでがちです。申し訳ない。素材足りない）

　

廃校をリノベーションした宿泊施設とか撮影スタジオがあるんですが、グループで借りればそこそこ納得のお値段で修学旅行気分やコスプレして学生気分が味わえます。学習用素材つくるために撮影ツアーとか行きたいですね…。

　

打率が微妙なので場所別で再学習させました。

学校の廊下（SDXL)→https://civitai.com/models/136158/sdxl

学校の階段（SDXL)→https://civitai.com/models/136153/sdxl

items.name: Comic Babes
items.description:
April 19 2023 Update:

First of all, thank you so much for 1,000 likes (and counting)! I had no idea this model would do so well. I just found myself using it all the time and decided to share it. It makes me happy that so many people enjoy it! And, I hope this encourages you to share your ai assets with the community as well!

Also, I added version 1.0 Baked Vae. It's the same as the original version, just includes the anything v4 vae. I was getting consistent results with this baked version, and decided to share it with the community! Can't wait to see your images!

A model I merged that I just keep coming back to, so I decided to share it.

A 50/50 blend of iCoMix v1 and Babes v1.1. Recommended you use a vae. I use anything_v4, which is available for download here.

EasyNegative also works very well with this merge, and minimal negative prompts tend to produce nice results.

I'm already working on some other versions that incorporate new versions of iCoMix and Babes.

Please share your images! I'd love to see what you create.

Thanks to lostdog and alexds9 for their terrific models.

Description:

A LoRA mixed model of my earlier 餃子Mix. This checkpoint kind of puts the whole picture through a monochromatic filter reminiscent of the 水墨畫 style calligraphy used in Sinosphere traditional paintings. It has an extremely heavy effect on trees and landscapes, where the leaves turn into the ink blotting reminiscent of calligraphy painting. Less-so on the characters, as a result the tuning ratio has been adjusted to preserve the anime-esque style of the characters.

Originally I was going to name it 虾饺Mix because I love shrimp jiaozi, but since I added a bit of the 伢伢書 LoRA, I figured I'd make it more Shanghai-esque (plus I had wontons for lunch yesterday). Hence, 三餡馄饨Mix.

Versions:

As of now there are 3 versions. Base, Anime, and MSG. Base is just GyozaMix with a light filter. It's okay to take in LoRAs. Season to your taste. Clothing and character LoRAs are more compatible. MSG edition is more 水墨畫. I basically turned up the loras in strength until it stopped looking good and then took a step back from that. Stylistic effect is very strong, but it's still recognizably illustrative. Anime is my personal favorite. It's more aesthetically 水墨畫 with all that entails but also retains those classic anime style features beneath all the watercolor ink art. You can try style loras on it but to be honest it's not as versatile as base and might collapse.

Usage Notes:

I recommend you be a bit careful of using Latent upscaler at high denoise. Because the model is a bit heavily opinionated given the style goal and such, at high denoise it tends to shoot strongly to turn it into a real Chinese watercolor painting and thus heavily changes the original image.

With MSG edition, you need to prompt for realism or else the shuimobyhua effect will be too strong. A good style to try is:

(ultra high res,photorealistic,realistic,best quality,photo-realistic),
(high detailed skin,visible pores),(real person,photograph),
(8k, raw photo, best quality, masterpiece)

All images here were generated with Store Bought Gyoza Mix v1.0 and the badhandv4 embedding. I'm running with xformers enabled, so your generations may be inconsistent with mine, but the general styles should match.

With the exception of the first sample image for each LoRA, sample images are not cherry-picked.

All LoRAs are optimized for strength 1.0.

Note that the later versions aren't intended to be "better" or more advanced. They're all just different styles. Download them all! :)

items.name: Sangonomiya Kokomi 珊瑚宫心海
items.description:
使用说明

触发词 Sangonomiya\(Genshin\)，即使不添加触发词，模型仍然可以正常工作，但效果不佳。

可以使用 underwater, sea, ocean 增加水下效果

如果你的画面背景出现了水滴，可以尝试在负面提示词内加入 underwater, sea, ocean，推荐负面提示词常驻 underwater

更换服装

更换服装时可以加入关键字 adapted costume，效果不佳时可提高提示词权重

dress 等衣服类的权重 推荐范围1.0 - 1.5

adapted costume 的权重 推荐范围1.0 - 1.3

no socks, pantyhose 等袜子权重 推荐 1.1 左右

high heels 等鞋子权重无需调整

另一些底模型则需要更高的参数（1.5 以上）

推荐参数

模型权重：0.7-1.0

Guide

prompt word 'Sangonomiya\(Genshin\)'. Even without adding trigger words, the model still works, but not good enough.

You can use 'underwater, sea, ocean' to increase the underwater effect

If there are water droplets in the background of your screen, you can try to add 'underwater, sea, ocean' to the negative prompt words, and it is recommended that the negative prompt words always addo underwater

Change clothes

The keyword 'adapted costume' can be added when changing clothes and the weight of the prompt word can be increased when the effect is not good

The weight of clothes such as 'dress', the recommended range is 1.0 - 1.5

The weight of adapted costume recommended range 1.0 - 1.3

'No socks, pantyhose' and other socks weight recommended around 1.1

'High heels' and other shoe weights do not need to be adjusted

Other bass models require higher parameters (Over 1.5)

Recommended parameters

Model Weight: 0.7-1.0

items.name: Girls With Pecs
items.description:
This LoRA was trained to render beautiful girls with pectoral muscles (instead of breasts). Have fun!

The starting model was Clarity, and all examples were rendered using it. It seems to work better when the prompt includes muscular, toned, fit, developed or similar. Also, prompts for soft faces and features (and negative prompt for sharp features) help draw better looking faces.

It does full nudity too, but it's not very consistent (some re-training may help). It also works with Anime model (see last example, using Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix).

Note that this is obviously NOT a realistic model of female bodybuilders or small-chested girls.

items.name: Sloppy Fellatio LoRA
items.description:
This is my Fellatio LoRA, with an emphasis on spit and fluid depiction. Great with semen as well. It's prone to blowjobs viewed from the side, rather than a POV of the crotch. If you want a crotch POV, then put 'pov, crotch pov' in your tags.

The weight is good from 0.6 to 0.8, but I use 0.75 weight. Sometimes the images produce extra fingers / fingers without arms on penises. For this, inpainting will work to remove them.

If your model has a problem with penises, hands, and fellatio adjacent subjects, then it will have problems with this. The trigger words are "saliva, sloppy fellatio, fellatio".

All pics were made with my custom blends with Hires Fix and orangemix VAE. The LoRA was trained off of NovelAI, so naturally it'll work with most anime-based models.

items.name: Shuna (Tensura) Character LoRA
items.description:
Shuna Character LoRA

If you enjoy my models and want to support me you could buy me a coffee!

This LoRA mimics the character Shuna from That Time I Reincarnated as a Slime.

The example images were created with NeverEndingDream, AbyssOrangeMix and Dual Personality on varying weight but feel free to experiment on your own. I tried briefly to mix it with a couple of different embeddings and it gave back decent results but you might find a better way to mix them (changing different weights etc.).

To change the weight just change the '1' in this prompt: <lora:shuna-LoRA:1>.

I'd love to see the art you guys make with it so feel free to add them in comments.

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight (by default it's :1 which is usually too high)
